Comment: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:23.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:27.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Courage is in two worlds\Nそう Together now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:27.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「proof！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「それが　二つ　結ぶ絆だから」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Everyone smiles at the beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:34.83,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「my dream！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「明日の扉の向こう期待しちゃう」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:38.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「alone！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:44.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,もしも月のない　空に星が輝いても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:45.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「no magic！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:51.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,もしも太陽が無い　空の雲が流れてても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:54.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,淋しそうに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.78,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,当たり前に　隣に居た
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:23:01.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,君を探してる二人映る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:02.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,『frame Decorate』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,思うがままワガまま　ありのままに並べよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:10.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,相性『Plus＋ Minus－ Multiply× Divide÷ 』by
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:10.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,全部好き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Calling me Calling you (and you)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:18.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,君と歩きたい未来階段（stairs）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Lucky Lucky Shiny 二人の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ときめきDreamin'　明日晴れ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:25.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,なら　万事オーライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:28.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ちょっとブルー　Weakness「but happy」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:32.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,けど君が居るから　Being saved
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,無駄な時間なんて無い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:35.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,雨上がる空をWaiting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Check it out　見上げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:42.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Courage is in two worlds\Nそう Together now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:44.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「proof！」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:46.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「それが　二つ　結ぶ絆だから」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:49.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Everyone smiles at the beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「どんな明日を照らすのかな？ スポットライト」
Comment: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:23.53,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:27.11,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,勇气两个世界都在\N所以是时候一起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:27.88,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「证据」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「就是紧系你我的羁绊」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.94,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,每个人都对漂亮的少女微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:34.83,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「我的梦想」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.71,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「不禁期待明天之后会是怎样」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:38.38,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「一人」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:44.31,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,纵使月色淡去 繁星也能闪耀夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:45.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「无关魔法」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:51.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,即便太阳不在 云朵也湍流在天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:54.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,与寂寞陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.78,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,理所当然地 守护在彼此身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:23:01.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,寻找你的身音 把两人倒映
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:02.49,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,盛装点缀于画框
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.70,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,随心所欲 撒娇任性 就这原原本本地并列吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:10.16,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,契合度是「加减乘除」的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:10.99,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,全都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.46,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,呼唤感召你与我（你也一样）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:18.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,想和你一同登上未来的阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,幸运有趣阳光的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.01,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,怦然心动的梦境 明日肯定天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:25.01,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,如此万事都行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:28.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,情绪微蓝 稍怕懦弱「但很幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:32.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,因有你在得到了救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,绝没有时间被虚度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:35.98,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,不过等候雨过天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,抬起头 快来看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:42.82,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,勇气两个世界都在\N所以是时候一起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:44.33,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「证据」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:46.65,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「就是紧系你我的羁绊」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:49.92,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,每个人都对漂亮的少女微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.19,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「聚光灯下 映照的明天又能怎样」
Comment: 1,0:00:19.21,0:00:22.21,main-JP,,0,0,0,,beforeop
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.21,0:00:25.67,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,信じられない　明日から新学期だなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.97,0:00:31.97,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,風　夏休みの宿題は終わったの
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.06,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ギリギリで終わったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.06,0:00:37.06,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,それなら　明日のテストも安心ね
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.06,0:00:38.60,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,え　テスト
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.98,0:00:42.56,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,伊呂波ちゃんから聞いたよ　休み明けにあるって
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.19,0:00:45.11,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,忘れてた
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.07,0:00:52.53,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,塔子さんからだ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.37,0:00:56.04,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えっと　いきなりだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.04,0:00:58.20,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,明日スケジュール空いてない
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.20,0:01:01.54,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ARSテレビからリリィに出演依頼が来たの
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.54,0:01:05.96,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,「どうしてもリリィに出てほしい」って
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.96,0:01:08.34,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ええ　明日は無理
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.55,0:01:13.18,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,だよね　断っとく　急にごめんね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.39,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.39,0:01:19.06,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,明日番組に出られないかって
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.06,0:01:21.27,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そんなのできるわけないじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.27,0:01:22.85,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,明日テストだし
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.48,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.48,0:01:29.69,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,宿題にアイドルに忙しいのに　テストまで
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.20,0:01:34.07,main-JP,fuu,0,0,0,,もうやってらない
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.66,0:01:37.54,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリルラ　パリルラ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.54,0:01:40.33,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,テストのない世界になーれ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.75,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,これでよし
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.09,0:01:49.01,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,なるかな
Comment: 1,0:03:24.98,0:03:25.81,main-JP,,0,0,0,,main
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.81,0:03:26.98,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,行ってきます
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.98,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,行ってらっしゃい　気を付けてね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.73,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,ほら　風も急がないと
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.74,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,わかってるー
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.95,0:03:42.58,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お願いです　魔法を聞いていてください
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.09,main-JP,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,野々山さん　遅いですよ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.00,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　はい
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.76,0:03:59.34,main-JP,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,え　早速ですが　今日から新学期ですね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.34,0:04:03.26,main-JP,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,久しぶりに元気な皆さんの顔が見られて嬉しいです
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.56,main-JP,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,さて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.68,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ダメダメ　テストはやめて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.06,main-JP,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,お知らせです
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.98,main-JP,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,これから学校ではテストはしません
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.69,0:04:16.61,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.07,main-JP,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,授業もやりません
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.07,0:04:18.70,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.78,main-JP,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,各自　好きに過ごしてくださいね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.74,main-JP,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.95,0:04:31.04,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,嘘　テストどころか授業もなくなっちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.00,main-JP,Kid,0,0,0,,やほう！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.68,0:04:41.64,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,ねえねえ　なにする
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.43,main-JP,Hayato,0,0,0,,みんなでメダカ屋行こうぜ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.43,0:04:44.81,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,賛成
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.81,0:04:45.43,main-JP,Hayato,0,0,0,,行こうぜ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.64,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,メダカ屋って学校の外だけど
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.81,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,ねえねえ　風ちゃんも行こうよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.81,0:04:52.86,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.32,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,まあいいか　行く
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.33,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,これは一体
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.75,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,先生も全然来ないし
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.51,0:05:21.72,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あの　おはよう
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.85,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,流ちゃん　おはよう
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.22,0:05:28.22,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,今日　その　なんか変じゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.56,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,そんなことないよね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.60,main-JP,Momo,0,0,0,,うん　これが普通だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.86,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,でも　どうして授業がないの
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.11,main-JP,Momo,0,0,0,,野々山さん　大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.15,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,もしかして具合悪い
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.24,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ううん　大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.74,0:05:51.87,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,本当に授業ないんだ　みんな遊んでるし
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.08,main-JP,Classmate,0,0,0,,この後さ公園も行こうよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.54,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,ああ、いいね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.80,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,学校の外に出ちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.51,main-JP,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}天気は良いよな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.51,0:06:00.13,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,{\an8}ねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.38,main-JP,Classmate,0,0,0,,{\an8}ちょうど熱い
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.80,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,あの雲　鳥みたい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.39,main-JP,Hayato,0,0,0,,え　どれのこと
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.43,main-JP,Classmate,0,0,0,,バナナに見えるかも
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.56,main-JP,Hayato,0,0,0,,バナナ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.47,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,あっちは
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.39,main-JP,Hayato,0,0,0,,あっ　あれはカニ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.52,main-JP,Hayato,0,0,0,,なあ　メダカ屋で何買う
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.52,0:06:14.48,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,きなこ棒
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.98,main-JP,Classmate,0,0,0,,ジュース飲みたい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.11,main-JP,Hayato,0,0,0,,あでも　暑いからアイス…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.65,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うぐいす　魔法　成功した
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.19,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,めーつらしいな
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.40,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.66,main-JP,Hayato,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.66,0:06:27.07,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,風ちゃん　行こうよ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.12,main-JP,Hayato,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.66,0:06:30.33,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんでもない
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.17,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,来ちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.09,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,本当はまだ授業中なのに
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.81,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,やっぱり変　こんなことがあるなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.44,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,前にもあったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.44,0:07:00.98,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,もしかして魔法の国の人のいたずらなのかも
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.69,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ねえ　あずき
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.82,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,そう　かもね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.24,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,どうしてこんないたずら
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.58,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,学校は勉強するところなのに
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.71,0:07:24.30,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,角谷　俺たちこれでいいんだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.59,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,いいんじゃね　てか遊び行こうぜ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.60,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.39,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,新しいシューズ欲しいんだよな
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.81,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,わかるー　でも金がない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.61,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,なあ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.03,0:07:43.78,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.53,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　翔ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.24,0:07:51.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,てえねえ翔ちゃん　どこ行くの　一緒に遊ぼうよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.62,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,悪い　今は忙しい
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.87,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えぇー
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.62,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,そうだっき
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.29,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,また今度な
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.92,0:08:00.75,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.09,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,ごめんな
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.30,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もー
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.34,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,翔ちゃん　いつも忙しいじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.05,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,行くよー
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.47,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,誰もいないよね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.18,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.27,0:08:19.31,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,誰のいたずらかわからないけど　元に戻さないと
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.44,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,そうね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.94,0:08:21.69,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,デット
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.03,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ルルリラ　プルリラ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.41,0:08:35.37,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あるべき世界に戻ってー
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.37,0:08:37.87,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,頑張れー
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.38,main-JP,Iroha,0,0,0,,あっ　これもいいね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.97,main-JP,Classmate,0,0,0,,どれにしよっかな
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.38,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.85,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あった　おみくじグミ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.97,0:08:54.56,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.97,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,これくーださーい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.27,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,まいど
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.98,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そうで
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.94,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,今日の運勢はどうかな
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.53,0:09:08.44,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.57,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なにこれ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.57,0:09:14.83,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,図形の面積を求めましょう
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.83,0:09:18.04,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おみくじじゃない　どういうこと
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.79,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,テストだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.67,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,問題に答えて
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.05,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そんな　いきなり
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.34,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ねえ　みんな
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.59,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,みんなー
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.64,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,さあ　はやく
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.31,0:09:40.23,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もう　やーだー
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.64,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,待ちなさーい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.35,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いやー
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.81,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,ほら　待てー
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.86,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,あの子どこ行ったのか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.33,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,追いかけてきてる
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.58,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うぐいす　どうしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.58,0:10:00.29,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,どうしよっか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.33,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もう
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.96,0:10:03.83,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リット
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.93,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリレラ　パリレラ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.51,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,パムパムパワー
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.95,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,どこへ行ったのか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.24,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,ねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.53,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　は　はい
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.53,0:10:43.37,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,あなた　この近くで10歳くらいの女の子見なかったかい
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.04,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いえ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.71,main-JP,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,あっちかね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.92,0:10:54.13,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんとかごまかせた
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.14,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,はあ　びっくりした
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.14,0:11:00.39,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ほんとだよ　駄菓子屋でテストなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.14,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,おかしいな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.14,0:11:05.19,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もしかして魔法が解けちゃったのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.69,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,よーし　もう一回
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.02,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うぐいす　見張ってて
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.94,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリレラ　パリレラ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.90,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,今度こそテストをなくして
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.58,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,こら
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.37,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,静かにしろ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.21,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,{\an8}今日はやけに騒がしいな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.42,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,{\an8}授業を始めるぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.42,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,よかった、みんな元に戻ったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.96,0:11:33.30,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,ええ　今日は実力テストをやろう
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.51,0:11:38.76,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,みんなどうした　黙って座ったりして
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.60,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,何かあるのか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.93,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,なんだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.10,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.23,main-JP,Student 1,0,0,0,,なんで座ってるんだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.69,main-JP,Student 2,0,0,0,,わかんない
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.65,main-JP,Student 1,0,0,0,,まあいっか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.65,0:11:48.60,main-JP,Student 2,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.94,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,じゃあ　先生は帰るから
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.98,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,みんなも好きなようにしなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.78,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ま　待ってください　テストは
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.53,0:11:59.53,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,テスト　野々山　何を言ってるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.49,main-JP,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.29,main-JP,Momo,0,0,0,,私たちも帰ろっか
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.04,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.05,0:12:16.22,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,そんな　どうして
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.81,0:12:23.81,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あずき
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.81,0:12:27.60,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,魔法を誰かに押し負けちゃったのかも
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.56,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,流がんばって
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.56,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,うん　負けない
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.53,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,リリィ　あの仕事やっぱり無理だって
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.53,0:12:40.07,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ああ　テレビの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.07,0:12:42.32,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,うん　予定あるみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.66,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,おととい話が来て　今日収録だって
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.66,0:12:49.04,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,一応聞いてみたけどさすがにないよね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.21,0:12:54.00,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,でもあの子　いつも何してるんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.05,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,さてねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.05,0:13:00.01,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,お　授業始まるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.01,0:13:00.76,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.77,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,きっと誰かの仕業なんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.02,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,ファイトー
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.44,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ルルリラ　プルリラ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.44,0:13:17.74,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,お願い　魔法の邪魔をやめさせて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.70,0:13:22.91,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,みんなのとこ戻らないの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.91,0:13:26.49,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,だって　また魔法が聞いてなかったら怖いもん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.70,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,いたいた
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.71,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,リリィさん　やっと見つけましたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.67,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,ARSテレビです
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.67,0:13:37.21,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,リリィさんにどうしてもご出演をお願いしたくて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.92,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,ここまで来てしまいました
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.92,0:13:42.18,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,え　もしかして昨日の
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.51,0:13:45.26,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,無理無理　無理ですってば
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.89,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,あ　そこぜひ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.97,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,とりあえず撮っちゃいましょう
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.97,0:13:50.98,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,はい　3　2
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.98,0:13:53.85,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ダメだってば　もう
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.77,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,あ　待ってください　リリィさん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.45,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おいで来ないでー
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.83,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,あれって
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.62,0:14:12.62,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,翔太　カラオケに何歌う
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.00,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,翔太　おい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.38,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,ごめん　ちょっと先行ってて
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.88,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,おい　翔太
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.30,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,待ってくださーい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.68,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,カメラテストお願いしまーす
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.85,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,だからテストは嫌なんだってば
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.97,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,リリィさん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.14,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,こっち
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.98,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,翔ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.53,0:14:41.94,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,リリィさん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.61,main-JP,Cameraman,0,0,0,,あれ　どこ行った
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.74,main-JP,Boom Operator,0,0,0,,向こう側も
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.45,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,行ったか
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.45,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.24,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.24,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,手
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.12,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.37,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,アイドルのリリィさんですよね
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.42,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,あの　なんでこんなところに
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.34,0:15:02.38,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,アイドルもたまには羽を伸ばしたいんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.38,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,ああ　やっぱり大変ですもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.34,0:15:09.39,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ごめんね　君も忙しいのに
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.26,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.89,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,大丈夫　全然暇してました
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.31,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そうなの
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.90,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,さっきは忙しいって言ってたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.27,0:15:22.65,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,俺　前に渋谷に行った時にリリィさんのステージを見て
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.99,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,それですごいファンになったんです
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.66,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あの時　声かけてくれたよね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.03,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,覚えててくれたんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.03,0:15:35.25,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,この前のクイズ番組も見ました　なんかすごかったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.25,0:15:36.96,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ああ　あれね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.96,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,リリィさん
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.84,main-JP,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{\an8}もうカメラ待ってましょう
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.92,0:15:41.84,main-JP,Boom Operator,0,0,0,,出てきてください
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.17,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,また戻ってきた
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.51,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,あっちへ逃げましょう
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.51,0:15:46.13,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.38,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,急いで
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.57,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,やれやれ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.64,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,おい　待ってくださーい
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.02,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もう　いい加減にして
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.48,0:16:02.02,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,リリィさーん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.78,main-JP,Cameraman,0,0,0,,もう
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.20,main-JP,Boom Operator,0,0,0,,走れない
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.45,main-JP,TV Director,0,0,0,,もう　ダメだー
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.46,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,諦めてくれたかな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.13,0:16:21.96,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ん　どうしたの
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.71,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,あっ　いえ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.80,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,本当にリリィさんなんだなって
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.80,0:16:30.59,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,今頃になって　やっと時間が
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.97,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,翔太
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.39,0:16:35.85,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,いきなりどこ行ってたんだよ　探したじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.81,0:16:37.85,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.85,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,リ　リリィちゃん　まじで
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.48,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,おい　騒ぐな　追われてるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.36,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,誰もいません
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.36,0:16:51.03,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,それらしい奴は来てませんね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.03,0:16:53.12,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,本当に　もう大丈夫ですか
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.12,0:16:57.96,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん　ちゃんと断ったって事務所から今連絡が来た
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.46,0:17:00.71,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,ちょっと待ってて
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.46,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,翔ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.09,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,これ　使ってくださ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.09,0:17:08.97,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.05,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,だって　そのままじゃ目立つから
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.26,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　変装よ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.26,0:17:17.35,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,お前　そんな親切な奴だったっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.02,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,うるさい
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.48,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.90,0:17:24.73,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,じゃあ　私はこれで
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.98,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,あ　その前に　サインください
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.28,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,お　俺も
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.07,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん　いいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.62,0:17:39.20,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,君　かっこよかったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.21,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,じゃあね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.34,0:17:52.34,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,リリィちゃんかっこいい　ますますファンになったわ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.34,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,だな
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.18,0:18:03.02,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,翔ちゃんたちの反応　面白かったな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.02,0:18:06.69,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,中身は私なのにあんなに真っ赤になっちゃって
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.90,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,疲れたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.57,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そうだね　いっぱい遊んだし帰ろっか
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.20,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,でも　まだ何か足りないような
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリルラ　パリルラ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.98,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,どこ行くの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.98,0:18:45.02,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,着いてからのお楽しみ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.78,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,急がないと　日が暮れちゃう
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.61,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,まだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もうちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,到着
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.28,0:19:01.28,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,おっと
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.42,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,着いた
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.76,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,ここ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.89,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん　昔お姉ちゃんと来てたの
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.60,0:19:24.69,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,一緒に走ったり歌ったり　楽しかったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.69,0:19:25.89,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,うーん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.82,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　あぶなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.86,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.55,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,夏が終わったのに
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.43,0:19:58.64,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,魔法だ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.81,0:20:10.11,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いいなあ　こういうの久しぶり
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.90,0:20:16.70,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}キラキラの大空で
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.70,0:20:21.45,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}お星さまにのった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.45,0:20:26.04,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}ふわふわの雲が
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}わたあめみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.42,0:20:36.30,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}いちにのさんでかけだして
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.30,0:20:41.14,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}いちばんぼうしつかまえた
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.14,0:20:46.10,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}わたしたちきらきら
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.10,0:20:50.06,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}ずっとなかよし
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.11,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,何の歌
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.57,0:20:58.95,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんと一緒に作った歌
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.95,0:20:59.91,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.07,0:21:05.41,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,学校もアイドルも全部投げ出しちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.66,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,明日からどうしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.75,0:21:10.75,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いた
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.92,0:21:13.34,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,アイスだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.13,0:21:18.76,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そっか　私これが食べたかったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.39,0:21:27.14,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,結局みんな帰っちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.60,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,もう帰ろ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.60,0:21:29.60,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.60,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,でも最後にもう一回だけ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.32,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ルルリラ　プルリラ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.32,0:21:38.99,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,お願い　今度こそあるべき世界に戻って
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.91,0:21:48.87,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,魔法　終わったね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.62,0:21:51.37,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.42,0:21:53.88,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,帰ろっか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.71,0:21:59.55,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,風　流　さっき学校から連絡があってね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.97,0:22:04.01,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,今日のテストは明日改めてやることになって
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.01,0:22:06.85,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ええ　やっぱりあるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.85,0:22:07.81,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.52,0:22:10.31,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,こうしちゃやれない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.31,main-JP,Ugusiu,0,0,0,,どうするの
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.98,0:22:16.98,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,もしかして
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.98,0:22:19.48,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,明日もテスト無くす
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.48,0:22:22.99,main-JP,Uguisu/Azuki,0,0,0,,辞めて！
Comment: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:22.21,main-CN,,0,0,0,,beforeop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:25.67,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,难以置信 明天就是新学期了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:31.97,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,风 暑假作业写完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.06,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,勉勉强强写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:37.06,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,既然如此 明天的测试就能放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:38.60,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶 测试
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:42.56,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,我听伊吕波说的 假期结束后就开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:45.11,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:52.53,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,是塔子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:56.04,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那个 有点突然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:58.20,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,明天你有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:01.54,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,ARS电视台给莉莉发来了演出邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:05.96,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,无论如何都希望莉莉出演
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:08.34,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶 明天不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:13.18,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,是啊 那我拒绝了 突然找你很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.39,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:19.06,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,说是明天能否出演一期节目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:21.27,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这明明是做不到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:22.85,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,毕竟明天有测试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.48,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:29.69,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,写作业还有当偶像忙死了 还有测试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:34.07,main-CN,fuu,0,0,0,,我忍不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:37.54,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪礼露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:40.33,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,让世界再也没有测试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.75,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:49.01,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,会成功吗
Comment: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:25.81,main-CN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:26.98,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.98,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,一路顺风 路上要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.73,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,风也是快点出发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.74,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:42.58,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,拜托了 魔法请倾听我的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.09,main-CN,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,野野山同学 你迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.00,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:59.34,main-CN,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,那么事不宜迟 今天就是新学期了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:03.26,main-CN,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,能看到大家充满活力的笑容 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.56,main-CN,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.68,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不行不行 不要测试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.06,main-CN,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,有个通知要告知大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.98,main-CN,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,今后学校不会进行测试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:16.61,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.07,main-CN,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,也不上课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:18.70,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.78,main-CN,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,请大家随心所欲地度过校园时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.74,main-CN,Fuu's Teacher,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:31.04,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不是吧 不光是测试连课都不用上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.00,main-CN,Kid,0,0,0,,好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:41.64,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,呐呐 做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.43,main-CN,Hayato,0,0,0,,大家一起去青鳉零食店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:44.81,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:45.43,main-CN,Hayato,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.64,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,可是青鳉零食店在学校外面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.81,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,呐呐 小风也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:52.86,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.32,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不过也行 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.33,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,这到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.75,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,老师完全不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:21.72,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那个 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.85,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,流酱 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:28.22,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,今天 那个 难道不有点奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.56,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.60,main-CN,Momo,0,0,0,,嗯 这挺正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.86,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,但是 为什么不上课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.11,main-CN,Momo,0,0,0,,野野山同学 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.15,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,难不成身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.24,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,没有 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:51.87,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,真的不用上课了 大家都在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.08,main-CN,Classmate,0,0,0,,这之后我们去公园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.54,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,啊 行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.80,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,竟然出学校外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.51,main-CN,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}天气很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:00.13,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,{\an8}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.38,main-CN,Classmate,0,0,0,,{\an8}就是有点热
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.80,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,那朵云 像一只小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.39,main-CN,Hayato,0,0,0,,诶 哪朵云
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.43,main-CN,Classmate,0,0,0,,或许更像香蕉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.56,main-CN,Hayato,0,0,0,,香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.47,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,那边的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.39,main-CN,Hayato,0,0,0,,啊 有点像螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.52,main-CN,Hayato,0,0,0,,对了 青鳉零食店你要买什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:14.48,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,黄豆粉糖棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.98,main-CN,Classmate,0,0,0,,我想喝果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.11,main-CN,Hayato,0,0,0,,可是 太热了吃点冰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.65,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,豌豆 魔法成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.19,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,好稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.40,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.66,main-CN,Hayato,0,0,0,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:27.07,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,小风 走快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.12,main-CN,Hayato,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:30.33,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,没啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.17,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.09,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,实际上还在上课时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.81,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,果然还是很奇怪 竟然会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.44,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,之前也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:07:00.98,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,难不成又是魔法之国的家伙在恶作剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.69,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,呐 红豆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.82,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,可 能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.24,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,为什么要恶作剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.58,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,学校本应该是学习的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:24.30,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,角谷 我们这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.59,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,有啥不好 要不一起出去玩呗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.60,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.39,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,好想要新的鞋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.81,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,我懂 但是没有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.61,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:43.78,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.53,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 小翔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:51.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我说翔酱 你要去哪儿 和我们一起玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.62,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,抱歉 现在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.87,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.62,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.29,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,之后再玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:00.75,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.09,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.30,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.34,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,小翔 每次都说忙忙忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.05,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,我们要走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.47,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,没有人在对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.18,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:19.31,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是谁的恶作剧 但必须要恢复如初
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.44,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:21.69,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,黛特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.03,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,露露莉菈 蒲露莉菈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:35.37,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,快恢复到原来的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:37.87,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.38,main-CN,Iroha,0,0,0,,啊 这个也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.97,main-CN,Classmate,0,0,0,,要选哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.38,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.85,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,找到啦 抽签软糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:54.56,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.97,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.27,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,感谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.98,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那么看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.94,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,今天的运势如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:08.44,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.57,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:14.83,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,求图形的面积吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:18.04,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这不是抽签 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.79,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,是测试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.67,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,快点回答问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.05,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,怎么会 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.34,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,呐 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.59,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.64,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,行了快点作答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:40.23,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,真的是 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.64,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.35,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.81,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,喂 给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.86,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,那孩子去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.33,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,她追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.58,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,豌豆 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:00.29,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,你问我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.33,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:03.83,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.93,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪礼露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.51,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,帕姆帕姆力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.95,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,到底去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.24,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.53,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 您 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:43.37,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,在这附近 你有看见一个十岁的小女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.04,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.71,main-CN,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,会在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:54.13,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,总算是瞒过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.14,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,哈 吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:11:00.39,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,是真的啊 零食店竟然有测试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.14,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:05.19,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,难不成是魔法被解除了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.69,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.02,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,豌豆 帮我放风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.94,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪礼露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.90,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这次别再有测试了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.58,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.37,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,快安静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.21,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,{\an8}今天特别吵闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.42,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,{\an8}要开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.42,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,太好了 大家都恢复如初了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:33.30,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,那么 今天是水平测试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:38.76,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,大家怎么了 都这么安静坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.60,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.93,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.10,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.23,main-CN,Student 1,0,0,0,,为什么会坐在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.69,main-CN,Student 2,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.65,main-CN,Student 1,0,0,0,,不过算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:48.60,main-CN,Student 2,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.94,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,那么 老师我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.98,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,大家随便就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.78,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,请 请等一下 测试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:59.53,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,测试 野野山你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.49,main-CN,Rui's Teacher,0,0,0,,那么就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.29,main-CN,Momo,0,0,0,,我们也回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.04,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:16.22,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,怎么这样 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:23.81,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,红豆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:27.60,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,说不定比拼魔法失败了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.56,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,流 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.56,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,嗯 我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.53,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,莉莉 果然没办法参加那份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:40.07,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,啊 电视台的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:42.32,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,嗯 看起来她有安排
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.66,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,前天收到通知 今天就要录制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:49.04,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,姑且试着问了问 果然是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:54.00,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,但是那个孩子 平时都在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.05,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:00.01,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,啊 要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:00.76,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.77,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,肯定有人在背后搞鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.02,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.44,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,露露莉菈 蒲露莉菈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:17.74,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,拜托了 让捣乱魔法停止下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:22.91,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,不回去大家身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:26.49,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,可是万一魔法没有奏效 就很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.70,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.71,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,莉莉小姐 终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.67,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,我们是 ARS 电视台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:37.21,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,我们无论如何都希望莉莉小姐能够出演
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.92,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,所以就来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:42.18,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶 难不成是昨天那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:45.26,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不行不行 我现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.89,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,啊 这点请务必接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.97,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,总之我们先开始拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:50.98,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,好 三 二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:53.85,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,都说了不行 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.77,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,啊 请等一下 莉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.45,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不要过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.83,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,她是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:12.62,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,翔太 去卡拉OK选什么歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.00,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,翔太 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.38,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,抱歉 你先过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.88,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,喂 翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.30,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.68,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,请参加「摄影机测试」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.85,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我都说了我讨厌测试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.97,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,莉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.14,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.98,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,小翔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:41.94,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,莉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.61,main-CN,Cameraman,0,0,0,,啊嘞 她去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.74,main-CN,Boom Operator,0,0,0,,往这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.45,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,走掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.45,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.24,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.24,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.12,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.37,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,你是偶像莉莉小姐对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.42,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,那个 为什么你会在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:02.38,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,就算是偶像 有时也想随性玩一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.38,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,啊 果然你很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:09.39,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,抱歉 你也应该是比较忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.26,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.89,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,没事的 我现在很闲！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.31,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.90,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,明明刚刚还说很忙来着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:22.65,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,我之前去涩谷的时候 看到了莉莉的舞台表演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.99,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,然后就马上成为你的粉丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.66,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那个时候 你主动找我搭话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.03,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,你还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:35.25,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,我也看了之前的问答节目 虽然感觉很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:36.96,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.96,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,莉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.84,main-CN,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{\an8}相机已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:41.84,main-CN,Boom Operator,0,0,0,,请快点出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.17,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,又拐回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.51,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,我们往那边跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:46.13,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.38,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.57,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,诶呀诶呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.64,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,噢 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.02,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,真的是 适可而止啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:02.02,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,莉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.78,main-CN,Cameraman,0,0,0,,已经
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.20,main-CN,Boom Operator,0,0,0,,跑不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.45,main-CN,TV Director,0,0,0,,已经 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.46,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,他们有放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:21.96,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.71,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,啊 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.80,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,只是想到你真的是莉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:30.59,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,事到如今 好不容易有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.97,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:35.85,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,你突然跑哪里去了 我好找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:37.85,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.85,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,莉 莉莉小姐 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.48,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,喂 别这么大声 我们被人追着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.36,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,这里没有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:51.03,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,看起来那群人没有跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:53.12,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,你真的已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:57.96,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯 刚刚事务所发来信息说 已经明确拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:00.71,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.46,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,小翔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.09,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,这个 请使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:08.97,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.05,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,毕竟 你这样子太显眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.26,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 变装
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:17.35,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,你这家伙 真的有这么好心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.02,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.48,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:24.73,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那么 我也要告别啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.98,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,啊 在这之前 请帮我们签名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.28,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,我 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.07,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:39.20,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,你 很帅气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.21,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:52.34,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,莉莉酱好帅气 越来越喜欢她了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.34,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:03.02,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,小翔他们的反应真的好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:06.69,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,实际上明明是我 脸还红得跟苹果一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.90,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,累死我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.57,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,是啊 玩了好久 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.20,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,但是 总感觉还差点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪礼露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.98,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,你要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:45.02,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,到了之后就知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.78,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,再不快点 天就要黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.61,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:01.28,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,诶哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.42,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.76,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.89,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯 曾经和姐姐一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:24.69,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,一起在这里奔跑唱歌 那时候很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:25.89,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.82,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.86,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.55,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,明明夏天已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:58.64,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:10.11,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,真好 好久没有这样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:16.70,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}闪闪发光的晴空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:21.45,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}乘着星星飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:26.04,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}软软绵绵的云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}就像棉花糖一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:36.30,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}一二三嘿 跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:41.14,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}捉到第一颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:46.10,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}我们也要闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:50.06,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9EE8B&}情长意久远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.11,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,什么歌曲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:58.95,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我和姐姐一起作的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:20:59.91,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:05.41,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,学校还有偶像全都被我扔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.66,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,明天该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:10.75,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:13.34,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,是冰棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:18.76,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,对了 我一直都想吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:27.14,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,结果大家都回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.60,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,我们也回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:29.60,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.60,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,但是最后再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.32,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,露露莉菈 蒲露莉菈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:38.99,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,拜托了 这次一定要回到原来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:48.87,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,魔法 结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:51.37,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:53.88,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:59.55,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,风 流 刚刚学校来了信息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:04.01,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,今天的测试说是改到明天进行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:06.85,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶 果然还要测试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:07.81,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:10.31,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不能再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.31,main-CN,Ugusiu,0,0,0,,你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:16.98,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:19.48,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,明天也要消除测试
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:22.99,main-CN,Uguisu/Azuki,0,0,0,,不要啊！
